title: Music News: Coronavirus claims jazz great Manu Dibango
description: March 24, 2020: Jazz great Manu Dibango has died of COVID-19, and Radiohead's Ed O'Brien believes he is infected. Chris Thile talks about how the pandemic is affecting the musical life of New York City, while remote collaborations grow ever stranger.

title: Music News: remembering Kenny Rogers; streaming music numbers; Neil Diamond updates a beloved song
description:
March 23, 2020: Remembering Kenny Rogers; coronavirus pushes back album release dates; streaming music actually down; Neil Diamond updates lyrics to one of his most beloved songs.
